# XXX: This one is very weird. It shows something inside the icon theme in the stack,
# possibly even in an mmapped file which is not code. It does not depend on which module
# we register, we always get it once (not once per module) at the line which
# call the module's registration function. No module actuall calls g_path_get_dirname()
# there (AFAICT). Just ignore it.
{
    First module registering, but why? I am confused.
    Memcheck:Leak
    fun:malloc
    ...
    fun:g_path_get_dirname
    ...
    fun:register_module_with_info
}
